## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

{{#if has_npm}}
- Node.js >= 18.x
- npm or yarn
{{/if}}
{{#if has_pip}}
- Python >= 3.10
- pip or poetry
{{/if}}
{{#if has_docker}}
- Docker and Docker Compose
{{/if}}

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone {{github_url}}
cd {{repo_name}}

{{#if has_npm}}
# Install JavaScript dependencies
npm install
{{/if}}

{{#if has_pip}}
# Install Python dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
{{/if}}

{{#if has_docker}}
# Start with Docker
docker-compose up -d
{{/if}}
```

## Usage

```bash
{{#if has_npm}}
# Start development server
npm run dev
{{/if}}

{{#if has_pip}}
# Run the application
python main.py
{{/if}}
```

